{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864619786,"sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","part":{"id":"prt_d79c7a04d001l7YvrlBRWp9R3E","messageID":"msg_d79c79725001GaHGHDTD0pypq5","sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-0ba2eafed9904030bf64c7770e8055ce","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"ls -la /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/cli/","description":"List pkg/cli directory"},"output":"total 52\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:36 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 10 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:27 ..\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4968 Apr 11 07:31 agent_runtime_client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 2622 Apr 11 07:28 client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 3605 Apr 11 07:35 client_test.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4847 Apr 11 07:31 code_interpreter_client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4332 Apr 11 07:28 printer.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 1231 Apr 11 07:28 utils.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4310 Apr 11 07:36 utils_test.go\n","metadata":{"output":"total 52\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:36 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 10 root root 4096 Apr 11 07:27 ..\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4968 Apr 11 07:31 agent_runtime_client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 2622 Apr 11 07:28 client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 3605 Apr 11 07:35 client_test.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4847 Apr 11 07:31 code_interpreter_client.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4332 Apr 11 07:28 printer.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 1231 Apr 11 07:28 utils.go\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 4310 Apr 11 07:36 utils_test.go\n","exit":0,"description":"List pkg/cli directory","truncated":false},"title":"List pkg/cli directory","time":{"start":1775864619764,"end":1775864619785}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864619802,"sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","part":{"id":"prt_d79c7a2d7001TdoQwBNKI8OpUA","messageID":"msg_d79c79725001GaHGHDTD0pypq5","sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-94cda9a305fd4464a41d002ee15883cf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Command-line tool (`kubectl-agentcube`) for packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and checking status of AI agents against AgentCube or standard Kubernetes.\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: Global CLI options\n10: The system SHALL expose a Typer application named `agentcube` with global options on the root callback.\n11: \n12: #### Scenario: Version display\n13: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and importable\n14: - **WHEN** the user passes `--version` (eager option, `Optional[bool]`, default `None`)\n15: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `AgentCube CLI (kubectl agentcube) version: {__version__}` (Rich markup) and exit without running a subcommand (`typer.Exit()`), where `__version__` is `0.1.0` from `agentcube.__init__`\n16: \n17: #### Scenario: Global verbose logging\n18: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--verbose` / `-v` (`bool`, default `False`) on the root callback\n19: - **WHEN** the callback runs\n20: - **THEN** the system SHALL call `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`\n21: \n22: ### Requirement: `pack` command\n23: The system SHALL provide `pack` to validate and prepare a workspace, merge CLI overrides into metadata, optionally generate a `Dockerfile`, and report paths.\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\n26: - **GIVEN** the user runs `pack`\n27: - **WHEN** options are omitted\n28: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL use: `workspace` = `\".\"` (`-f` / `--workspace`, `str`); `agent_name` = `None` (`--agent-name`, `Optional[str]`); `language` = `None` (`--language`); `entrypoint` = `None` (`--entrypoint`); `port` = `None` (`--port`, `Optional[int]`); `build_mode` = `None` (`--build-mode`); `description` = `None` (`--description`); `output` = `None` (`--output`); `verbose` = `False` (`--verbose`, command-local)\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: Successful pack\n31: - **GIVEN** a valid workspace path\n32: - **WHEN** `pack` completes without exception\n33: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print success with `agent_name`, resolved `workspace_path`, and `metadata_path` (reported as `{final_workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml`), using a Rich `Progress` spinner during work\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Pack failure handling\n36: - **GIVEN** `PackRuntime.pack` raises\n37: - **WHEN** `verbose` is `True`\n38: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `Error packaging agent: {e}` in red, print a full traceback, and exit with code `1`\n39: \n40: ### Requirement: `build` command\n41: The system SHALL build a container image from a packaged workspace using local Docker when `build_mode` is `local` (default in metadata), with optional proxy and tag derived from metadata version.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\n44: - **GIVEN** the user runs `build`\n45: - **WHEN** options are omitted\n46: - **THEN** defaults SHALL be: `workspace` = `\".\"` (`-f` / `--workspace`); `proxy` = `None` (`-p` / `--proxy`); `cloud_provider` = `None` (`--cloud-provider`); `output` = `None` (`--output`); `verbose` = `False` (`--verbose`)\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Local Docker build prerequisites\n49: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` resolves to `local`\n50: - **WHEN** Docker is unavailable\n51: - **THEN** `BuildRuntime` SHALL raise `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")` surfaced via CLI error handling\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: Version increment on build\n54: - **GIVEN** a successful local build path\n55: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime.build` runs\n56: - **THEN** the system SHALL increment `metadata.version` (patch bump for `X.Y.Z`, or append `.1` / fallback `{version}-1`) before build and revert the version in metadata if build fails\n57: \n58: ### Requirement: `publish` command\n59: The system SHALL publish/deploy using provider `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) or `k8s` (Deployment + NodePort Service), preparing the image via Docker push or explicit image URL as implemented in `PublishRuntime`.\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\n62: - **GIVEN** the user runs `publish`\n63: - **THEN** defaults SHALL include: `workspace` = `\".\"`; `version` = `None` (`--version`); `image_url` = `None` (`--image-url`); `image_username` = `None` (`--image-username`); `image_password` = `None` (`--image-password`); `description` = `None`; `region` = `None` (`--region`); `cloud_provider` = `None`; `provider` = `\"agentcube\"` (`--provider`); `node_port` = `None` (`--node-port`, `Optional[int]`); `replicas` = `None` (`--replicas`); `namespace` = `None` (`--namespace`); `verbose` = `False`\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: AgentCube provider prerequisites\n66: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube`\n67: - **WHEN** metadata lacks `router_url` or `workload_manager_url`\n68: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with message requiring both fields in `agent_metadata.yaml`\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: Standard Kubernetes publish flow\n71: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `k8s` and Kubernetes client initializes\n72: - **WHEN** publish proceeds\n73: - **THEN** the system SHALL call `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent`, then `wait_for_deployment_ready(..., timeout=120)`, updating metadata with deployment info; on readiness failure it SHALL raise `RuntimeError` after recording error in metadata\n74: \n75: ### Requirement: `invoke` command\n76: The system SHALL POST JSON to the published agent endpoint, parse `--payload` as JSON, merge optional `--header` entries, and for AgentRuntime CR deployments rewrite the URL to `{base}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/` when `k8s_deployment.type == \"AgentRuntime\"`.\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\n79: - **GIVEN** the user runs `invoke`\n80: - **THEN** defaults SHALL be: `workspace` = `\".\"`; `payload` = `\"{}\"` (`--payload`, `str`); `header_list` = `None` (`--header`, repeatable `List[str]`); `provider` = `\"agentcube\"`; `verbose` = `False`\n81: \n82: #### Scenario: Invalid payload\n83: - **GIVEN** `payload` is not valid JSON\n84: - **WHEN** the command parses it\n85: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print invalid JSON in red and exit with code `1` (before `_handle_error`)\n86: \n87: #### Scenario: Invalid header format\n88: - **GIVEN** a header string without a single `:` separator\n89: - **WHEN** headers are parsed\n90: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print expected `key:value` format and exit with code `1`\n91: \n92: #### Scenario: Session header on invoke\n93: - **GIVEN** metadata contains `session_id`\n94: - **WHEN** `InvokeRuntime.invoke` runs\n95: - **THEN** the HTTP client SHALL add header `X-Agentcube-Session-Id` (same spelling as response handling) to the request\n96: \n97: ### Requirement: `status` command\n98: The system SHALL load workspace metadata and display agent status in a Rich `Table`, exiting with code `1` when status is `not_published` or `error`.\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\n101: - **GIVEN** the user runs `status`\n102: - **THEN** defaults SHALL be: `workspace` = `\".\"`; `provider` = `\"agentcube\"`; `verbose` = `False`\n103: \n104: #### Scenario: Not published\n105: - **GIVEN** metadata has no `agent_id`\n106: - **WHEN** `get_status` returns `status == \"not_published\"`\n107: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print guidance to publish first and exit with code `1`\n108: \n109: ### Requirement: Workspace validation (pack path)\n110: The system SHALL validate that the workspace path exists and is a directory; for Python, require at least one `*.py` file; for Java, require `pom.xml`.\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: Missing workspace\n113: - **GIVEN** `workspace_path` does not exist\n114: - **WHEN** `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure` runs\n115: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with a message that the directory does not exist\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: Python workspace without Python files\n118: - **GIVEN** `metadata.language == \"python\"`\n119: - **WHEN** no `*.py` exists in the workspace root\n120: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n121: \n122: ### Requirement: Metadata file format\n123: The system SHALL persist agent configuration as YAML. The primary filename SHALL be `agent_metadata.yaml`; loading SHALL fall back to `agent.yaml` then `metadata.yaml` if the primary file is missing.\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: Save location\n126: - **GIVEN** metadata is saved\n127: - **WHEN** `MetadataService.save_metadata` runs\n128: - **THEN** the file SHALL be written to `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml` using `yaml.dump` with `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`, excluding `None` fields via `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: Schema validation\n131: - **GIVEN** YAML is loaded\n132: - **WHEN** fields violate `AgentMetadata` validators\n133: - **THEN** Pydantic SHALL reject unsupported `language` / `build_mode` or invalid `port` range\n134: \n135: ### Requirement: Docker integration\n136: The system SHALL use the Docker SDK (`docker.from_env()`) to build images, push to a registry when configured, and optionally remove images.\n137: \n138: #### Scenario: Build image\n139: - **GIVEN** Docker is running\n140: - **WHEN** `DockerService.build_image` is called\n141: - **THEN** it SHALL tag `{image_name}:{tag}`, pass optional `buildargs` from proxy settings, and return `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: Push image\n144: - **GIVEN** a local image name and optional `registry_url` / credentials\n145: - **WHEN** `DockerService.push_image` runs\n146: - **THEN** it SHALL login if username and password are provided, retag when needed, stream push logs, and return `pushed_image` and `push_time`\n147: \n148: #### Scenario: Remove image\n149: - **GIVEN** `DockerService.remove_image(image_name)` is called\n150: - **WHEN** removal succeeds\n151: - **THEN** it SHALL return `True`; on failure it SHALL log a warning and return `False`\n152: \n153: ### Requirement: Kubernetes — standard provider\n154: The system SHALL create or patch `Deployment` and `NodePort` `Service`, wait for rollout, report pod status, and support deletion.\n155: \n156: #### Scenario: Deploy agent\n157: - **GIVEN** `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` is called\n158: - **WHEN** resources are applied\n159: - **THEN** the result SHALL include `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `replicas`, `container_port`, `node_port`, `service_url` as `http://localhost:{node_port}`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: Wait for ready\n162: - **GIVEN** a deployment name\n163: - **WHEN** `wait_for_deployment_ready` exceeds `timeout` seconds (default `120`)\n164: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `TimeoutError`\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: Delete agent\n167: - **GIVEN** `delete_agent` is called\n168: - **WHEN** deletion completes\n169: - **THEN** it SHALL return `{\"status\": \"deleted\", \"deployment_name\", \"namespace\"}` ignoring 404 on individual deletes\n170: \n171: ### Requirement: Kubernetes — AgentCube AgentRuntime CR\n172: The system SHALL create or patch an `AgentRuntime` custom object in group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`, plural `agentruntimes`.\n173: \n174: #### Scenario: Deploy CR\n175: - **GIVEN** required readiness probe fields exist in metadata\n176: - **WHEN** `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime` runs\n177: - **THEN** it SHALL embed `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL` from parameters or environment when missing in `env_vars`, set `sessionTimeout` to `\"15m\"` and `maxSessionDuration` to `\"8h\"`, and reference `imagePullSecrets` `[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]`\n178: \n179: ### Requirement: AgentCube provider integration (CLI)\n180: The system SHALL use `AgentCubeProvider` for `provider=agentcube` publish/status flows and `KubernetesProvider` for `provider=k8s`.\n181: \n182: #### Scenario: Status for AgentRuntime\n183: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube` and the CR exists\n184: - **WHEN** `StatusRuntime._get_cr_k8s_status` runs\n185: - **THEN** status SHALL be read from `cr_object[\"status\"]` when present (`status`, `agentEndpoint`), else `created_no_status`, else `not_found_in_k8s`\n186: \n187: ### Requirement: Error handling patterns\n188: The system SHALL use `_handle_error(e, command_name, verbose)` for subcommand exceptions: print `Error {command_name}: {e}` in red; if `verbose`, print traceback; raise `typer.Exit(1)`.\n189: \n190: #### Scenario: Subcommand verbose vs global verbose\n191: - **GIVEN** a subcommand’s local `--verbose` is `True` but global `-v` was not passed\n192: - **WHEN** an error occurs in that subcommand\n193: - **THEN** traceback SHALL still be printed because `_handle_error` receives the subcommand’s `verbose` flag\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: **Note:** The implementation uses `agent_metadata.yaml` as the canonical metadata filename (with `agent.yaml` / `metadata.yaml` fallbacks for load). Documentation that refers to `agentcube.yaml` SHALL be treated as naming drift unless a separate file is introduced in code.\n\n(End of file - total 197 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) Specification\n\n## Purpose\n\nCommand-line tool (`kubectl-agentcube`) for packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and checking status of AI agents against AgentCube or standard Kubernetes.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Global CLI options\nThe system SHALL expose a Typer application named `agentcube` with global options on the root callback.\n\n#### Scenario: Version display\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and importable\n- **WHEN** the user passes `--version` (eager option, `Optional[bool]`, default `None`)\n- **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `AgentCube CLI (kubectl agentcube) version: {__version__}` (Rich markup) and exit without running a subcommand (`typer.Exit()`), where `__version__` is `0.1.0` from `agentcube.__init__`\n\n#### Scenario: Global verbose logging\n- **GIVEN** the user passes `--verbose` / `-v` (`bool`, default `False`) on the root callback\n- **WHEN** the callback runs\n- **THEN** the system SHALL call `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md","time":{"start":1775864619769,"end":1775864619799}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775864619831,"sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","part":{"id":"prt_d79c7a319001QXvwPzaHKoKU8t","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d79c79725001GaHGHDTD0pypq5","sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":44373,"input":267,"output":139,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":43967}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775864627931,"sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","part":{"id":"prt_d79c7c2d9001Nm0pfCqqn8ne47","messageID":"msg_d79c7a3510014vsBstGMGdFcga","sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864717021,"sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","part":{"id":"prt_d79c91eb90018NFnq02qiovmSV","messageID":"msg_d79c7a3510014vsBstGMGdFcga","sessionID":"ses_28639230effeE9rb5ZWmOOlWZM","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-080157f9fc004cfa836207b5172fe7c4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-020: CLI pack 命令\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `pack` 命令，用于验证和准备 agent 工作区，合并 CLI 覆盖选项到元数据，可选生成 Dockerfile，并报告相关路径。这是 agent 生命周期管理的第一步，为后续的 build、publish、invoke 和 status 命令奠定基础。\n\n## Purpose\n\n`pack` 命令是 AgentCube CLI 工具的核心命令之一，负责：\n\n1. **工作区验证** - 确保工作区目录存在并包含必要的语言特定文件\n2. **元数据管理** - 加载、验证和更新 agent 配置（`agent_metadata.yaml`）\n3. **选项覆盖** - 允许通过 CLI 参数覆盖元数据中的配置项\n4. **依赖处理** - 识别和处理 Python 或 Java 项目依赖\n5. **Dockerfile 生成** - 根据语言和配置自动生成优化的 Dockerfile\n6. **路径报告** - 输出打包后的工作区路径和元数据文件路径\n\n该命令为开发者提供了简单、灵活的方式来准备 agent 工作区，确保其符合 AgentCube 平台的要求。\n\n## Module\n\n`cmd/cli` - Python CLI 工具包\n\n## Language\n\nPython 3.10+\n\n## Size\n\nM\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **PackRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`)\n   - `pack()` 方法 - 主打包逻辑\n   - `_validate_workspace_structure()` - 工作区结构验证\n   - `_load_or_create_metadata()` - 元数据加载或创建\n   - `_apply_option_overrides()` - CLI 选项覆盖\n   - `_validate_language_compatibility()` - 语言兼容性验证\n   - `_validate_python_compatibility()` - Python 工作区验证\n   - `_validate_java_compatibility()` - Java 工作区验证\n   - `_process_dependencies()` - 依赖处理\n   - `_process_python_dependencies()` - Python 依赖处理\n   - `_process_java_dependencies()` - Java 依赖处理\n   - `_generate_dockerfile()` - Dockerfile 生成\n   - `_generate_python_dockerfile()` - Python Dockerfile 生成\n   - `_generate_java_dockerfile()` - Java Dockerfile 生成\n   - `_update_pack_metadata()` - 更新打包元数据\n   - `_prepare_output_path()` - 准备输出路径\n   - `_infer_entrypoint()` - 推断入口点命令\n\n2. **CLI 命令定义** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - `pack()` 函数 - Typer 命令定义\n   - 支持所有必需的 CLI 选项\n   - 错误处理和用户反馈\n\n3. **元数据模型** (`agentcube/models/pack_models.py`)\n   - `MetadataOptions` 数据类 - CLI 选项封装\n   - 与 `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型的集成\n\n4. **Dockerfile 模板**\n   - Python 基础镜像选择（python:3.10-slim）\n   - Java 基础镜像选择（eclipse-temurin:17-jre）\n   - 优化的多阶段构建\n   - 端口暴露和健康检查配置\n\n5. **错误处理**\n   - 工作区不存在\n   - 缺少语言特定文件\n   - 无效的语言或构建模式\n   - 端口范围验证\n   - 依赖解析错误\n\n6. **Rich 输出**\n   - 进度条显示打包进度\n   - 成功消息带路径信息\n   - 错误消息带详细堆栈（verbose 模式）\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- `build` 命令 - Docker 镜像构建\n- `publish` 命令 - 发布和部署\n- `invoke` 命令 - agent 调用\n- `status` 命令 - 状态查询\n- 自定义 Dockerfile 模板（使用标准模板）\n- 非 Python/Java 语言支持\n- 远程依赖解析和下载\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Components Impacted\n\n1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\n   - 新增 `pack` 命令到 Typer 应用\n   - 集成 `PackRuntime` 类\n   - 更新错误处理逻辑\n\n2. **运行时包** (`agentcube/runtime`)\n   - 新增 `pack_runtime.py` 模块\n   - 与其他运行时类（`BuildRuntime`、`PublishRuntime` 等）保持一致性\n\n3. **服务包** (`agentcube/services`)\n   - `MetadataService` - 元数据加载和保存\n   - `DockerService` - Dockerfile 生成支持\n\n4. **模型包** (`agentcube/models`)\n   - 新增 `pack_models.py` 模块\n   - `MetadataOptions` 数据类\n\n5. **依赖管理**\n   - 新增 Python 依赖：`docker>=6.0.0`, `packaging>=23.0`\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `typer[all]` | >=0.9.0 | CLI 框架 |\n| `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | 数据验证 |\n| `pyyaml` | >=6.0 | YAML 处理 |\n| `docker` | >=6.0.0 | Docker SDK（用于验证） |\n| `rich` | >=13.0.0 | 富文本输出 |\n| `packaging` | >=23.0 | 版本解析 |\n\n### Security Considerations\n\n1. **路径安全**\n   - 验证工作区路径防止路径遍历攻击\n   - 限制访问权限，避免敏感信息泄露\n\n2. **元数据安全**\n   - 不在日志中输出敏感信息（密码、token）\n   - 支持环境变量覆盖敏感配置\n\n3. **依赖安全**\n   - 验证依赖文件来源（requirements.txt、pom.xml）\n   - 不执行依赖下载（由 build 命令处理）\n\n4. **Dockerfile 安全**\n   - 使用官方基础镜像\n   - 避免以 root 用户运行容器\n   - 最小化镜像层\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n### 语言选择\n\n**选择**: Python 3.10+\n\n**理由**:\n- 与现有 CLI 工具包保持一致\n- Typer 和 Rich 提供优秀的 CLI 开发体验\n- Pydantic 提供强大的数据验证\n- 易于维护和扩展\n\n### 元数据文件格式\n\n**选择**: YAML 格式，主文件名为 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n\n**理由**:\n- 人类可读和可编辑\n- 支持注释\n- 与 Kubernetes 生态一致\n- 支持回退加载（`agent.yaml`、`metadata.yaml`）\n\n### Dockerfile 生成策略\n\n**选择**: 自动生成，语言特定模板\n\n**理由**:\n- 减少用户手动配置\n- 确保最佳实践和安全配置\n- 支持快速迭代\n- 可通过 CLI 选项覆盖\n\n**Python Dockerfile 特性**:\n- 使用 `python:3.10-slim` 基础镜像\n- 多阶段构建减少镜像大小\n- 非 root 用户运行\n- 健康检查配置\n\n**Java Dockerfile 特性**:\n- 使用 `eclipse-temurin:17-jre` 基础镜像\n- 支持 JAR 文件部署\n- 优化的 JVM 参数\n- 健康检查配置\n\n### 选项覆盖策略\n\n**选择**: CLI 选项优先级高于元数据文件\n\n**理由**:\n- 支持快速原型开发\n- 便于 CI/CD 集成\n- 保持元数据文件作为默认配置\n\n**优先级顺序**:\n1. CLI 显式选项\n2. 环境变量\n3. 元数据文件值\n4. 默认值\n\n### 入口点推断策略\n\n**选择**: 智能推断，支持显式覆盖\n\n**理由**:\n- 减少配置负担\n- 支持常见项目结构\n- 保持灵活性\n\n**Python 推断规则**:\n- 检查 `main.py`、`app.py`、`server.py`\n- 使用 `python {file}` 作为入口点\n\n**Java 推断规则**:\n- 检查 `pom.xml` 中的主类\n- 使用 `java -jar {jar}` 作为入口点\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 仅支持手动配置 Dockerfile\n\n**描述**: 用户必须手动提供 Dockerfile\n\n**优点**:\n- 完全灵活\n- 无需模板管理\n\n**缺点**:\n- 增加用户负担\n- 容易出现配置错误\n- 难以保证一致性\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - 自动生成提供更好的用户体验\n\n### Alternative 2: 使用 JSON 而非 YAML\n\n**描述**: 元数据文件使用 JSON 格式\n\n**优点**:\n- 标准格式\n- 广泛支持\n\n**缺点**:\n- 不支持注释\n- 可读性差\n- 与 Kubernetes 生态不一致\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - YAML 更适合配置文件\n\n### Alternative 3: 支持所有 Python 版本\n\n**描述**: 支持多个 Python 版本（3.8、3.9、3.10、3.11）\n\n**优点**:\n- 灵活性高\n- 支持旧项目\n\n**缺点**:\n- 增加测试负担\n- 维护成本高\n- Dockerfile 模板复杂\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - 仅支持 Python 3.10+，保持简单\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: 基础结构 (Day 1)\n\n1. 创建 `cmd/cli` 目录结构\n2. 创建 `pyproject.toml` 配置文件\n3. 创建 `agentcube/__init__.py`\n4. 创建 `agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n5. 创建 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 框架\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] 目录结构创建\n- [ ] 依赖配置\n- [ ] Typer 应用初始化\n\n### Phase 2: 元数据模型 (Day 1-2)\n\n1. 创建 `agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n2. 创建 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n3. 实现 `MetadataOptions` 数据类\n4. 创建 `agentcube/models/metadata.py`（如果不存在）\n5. 实现 `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] `MetadataOptions` 实现\n- [ ] `AgentMetadata` 实现\n- [ ] 验证器实现\n- [ ] 单元测试\n\n### Phase 3: 元数据服务 (Day 2)\n\n1. 创建 `agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n2. 创建 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n3. 实现 `MetadataService` 类\n4. 实现加载、保存、更新方法\n5. 实现工作区验证方法\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] `MetadataService` 实现\n- [ ] 文件加载逻辑\n- [ ] 文件保存逻辑\n- [ ] 验证逻辑\n- [ ] 单元测试\n\n### Phase 4: PackRuntime 实现 (Day 2-4)\n\n1. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n2. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n3. 实现 `PackRuntime` 类\n4. 实现所有私有方法\n\n**关键方法**:\n```python\nclass PackRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self.logger = get_logger(__name__)\n\n    def pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"主打包方法\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def _validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None:\n        \"\"\"验证工作区结构\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def _load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n        \"\"\"加载或创建元数据\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def _apply_option_overrides(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n        \"\"\"应用选项覆盖\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def _validate_language_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        \"\"\"验证语言兼容性\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def _generate_dockerfile(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Optional[Path]:\n        \"\"\"生成 Dockerfile\"\"\"\n        pass\n```\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] `PackRuntime` 类实现\n- [ ] 工作区验证\n- [ ] 元数据处理\n- [ ] 依赖处理\n- [ ] Dockerfile 生成\n- [ ] 单元测试\n\n### Phase 5: CLI 命令集成 (Day 4)\n\n1. 在 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 中实现 `pack()` 命令\n2. 定义所有 CLI 选项\n3. 实现 Rich 进度显示\n4. 实现错误处理\n\n**命令签名**:\n```python\ndef pack(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n    agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", help=\"Override the agent name\"),\n    language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", help=\"Programming language (python, java)\"),\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", help=\"Override the entrypoint command\"),\n    port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--port\", help=\"Port to expose in the Dockerfile\"),\n    build_mode: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--build-mode\", help=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\"),\n    description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", help=\"Agent description\"),\n    output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for packaged workspace\"),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Pack an agent workspace for deployment.\"\"\"\n    pass\n```\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] CLI 命令实现\n- [ ] 选项定义\n- [ ] Rich 输出\n- [ ] 错误处理\n- [ ] 集成测试\n\n### Phase 6: Dockerfile 模板 (Day 5)\n\n1. 创建 Dockerfile 模板\n2. 实现 Python Dockerfile 生成\n3. 实现 Java Dockerfile 生成\n4. 优化镜像大小\n\n**Python Dockerfile 模板**:\n```dockerfile\nFROM python:3.10-slim as builder\n\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY requirements.txt .\nRUN pip install --user --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt\n\nFROM python:3.10-slim\n\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY --from=builder /root/.local /root/.local\nCOPY . .\n\nENV PATH=/root/.local/bin:$PATH\n\nEXPOSE {port}\n\nHEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n  CMD curl -f http://localhost:{port}/health || exit 1\n\nCMD {entrypoint}\n```\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] Python Dockerfile 模板\n- [ ] Java Dockerfile 模板\n- [ ] 优化和测试\n\n### Phase 7: 测试 (Day 5-6)\n\n1. 单元测试\n2. 集成测试\n3. 端到端测试\n\n**单元测试覆盖**:\n- `PackRuntime` 所有方法\n- `MetadataService` 所有方法\n- `MetadataOptions` 验证\n- 错误处理\n\n**集成测试**:\n- Python 工作区打包\n- Java 工作区打包\n- 选项覆盖\n- Dockerfile 生成\n\n**端到端测试**:\n- 完整打包流程\n- 输出验证\n- 元数据验证\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] 单元测试\n- [ ] 集成测试\n- [ ] 端到端测试\n- [ ] 覆盖率 > 80%\n\n### Phase 8: 文档 (Day 6-7)\n\n1. 添加 docstrings\n2. 创建示例\n3. 更新 README\n4. 添加使用指南\n\n**文档内容**:\n- API 文档\n- 使用示例\n- 命令参考\n- 最佳实践\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] API 文档\n- [ ] 使用示例\n- [ ] README 更新\n- [ ] 使用指南\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n1. **PackRuntime 测试**\n   - 工作区验证\n   - 元数据加载和创建\n   - 选项覆盖\n   - 语言兼容性验证\n   - 依赖处理\n   - Dockerfile 生成\n\n2. **MetadataService 测试**\n   - 文件加载（包括回退逻辑）\n   - 文件保存\n   - 元数据更新\n   - 工作区验证\n\n3. **MetadataOptions 测试**\n   - `from_options` 方法\n   - 字段验证\n   - 默认值\n\n4. **CLI 命令测试**\n   - 参数解析\n   - 错误处理\n   - 输出格式\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n1. **Python 项目打包**\n   - 简单 Python 项目\n   - 带依赖的 Python 项目\n   - 多文件 Python 项目\n\n2. **Java 项目打包**\n   - 简单 Java 项目\n   - 带 Maven 依赖的项目\n\n3. **选项覆盖**\n   - 所有 CLI 选项\n   - 组合选项\n   - 无效选项\n\n4. **Dockerfile 生成**\n   - Python Dockerfile\n   - Java Dockerfile\n   - 自定义端口和入口点\n\n### End-to-End Tests\n\n1. **完整打包流程**\n   - 创建工作区\n   - 运行 pack 命令\n   - 验证输出\n   - 验证元数据\n   - 验证 Dockerfile\n\n2. **错误场景**\n   - 工作区不存在\n   - 缺少 Python 文件\n   - 缺少 pom.xml\n   - 无效端口\n   - 无效语言\n\n### Test Coverage\n\n目标: > 80% 代码覆盖率\n\n## Configuration\n\n### CLI 选项\n\n| 选项 | 短选项 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|--------|------|\n| `--workspace` | `-f` | str | `\".\"` | 工作区目录路径 |\n| `--agent-name` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 覆盖 agent 名称 |\n| `--language` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 编程语言（python, java） |\n| `--entrypoint` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 覆盖入口点命令 |\n| `--port` | - | Optional[int] | `None` | Dockerfile 中暴露的端口 |\n| `--build-mode` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 构建策略（local, cloud） |\n| `--description` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | Agent 描述 |\n| `--output` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 打包工作区输出路径 |\n| `--verbose` | - | bool | `False` | 启用详细日志 |\n\n### 元数据字段\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `agent_name` | str | (required) | Agent 唯一名称 |\n| `description` | Optional[str] | `None` | 人类可读的摘要 |\n| `language` | str | `\"python\"` | 编程语言 |\n| `entrypoint` | str | (required) | 启动 agent 的命令 |\n| `port` | int | `8080` | agent runtime 暴露的端口 |\n| `build_mode` | str | `\"local\"` | 构建策略（local, cloud） |\n| `region` | Optional[str] | `None` | 部署区域 |\n| `version` | Optional[str] | `None` | 发布的语义版本字符串 |\n| `requirements_file` | Optional[str] | `\"requirements.txt\"` | Python 依赖文件 |\n\n### 环境变量\n\n| 环境变量 | 说明 |\n|---------|------|\n| `AGENTCUBE_VERBOSE` | 启用详细日志 |\n| `AGENTCUBE_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE` | 默认语言 |\n| `AGENTCUBE_DEFAULT_PORT` | 默认端口 |\n\n## API Specification\n\n### CLI 命令\n\n```bash\nkubectl-agentcube pack [OPTIONS]\n```\n\n### 输出格式\n\n**成功输出**:\n```\n✓ Successfully packed agent\n\nAgent Name: my-agent\nWorkspace: /path/to/workspace\nMetadata: /path/to/workspace/agent_metadata.yaml\nDockerfile: /path/to/workspace/Dockerfile\n```\n\n**错误输出**:\n```\n✗ Error packaging agent: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n```\n\n**详细错误输出** (verbose 模式):\n```\n✗ Error packaging agent: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/path/to/main.py\", line 42, in pack\n    result = runtime.pack(workspace_path, **options)\n  ...\nValueError: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n```\n\n### 元数据文件格式\n\n```yaml\nagent_name: my-agent\ndescription: A sample agent\nlanguage: python\nentrypoint: python main.py\nport: 8080\nbuild_mode: local\nregion: us-west-1\nversion: 1.0.0\nrequirements_file: requirements.txt\n```\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n1. **路径验证**\n   - 验证工作区路径在当前目录或子目录\n   - 防止路径遍历攻击\n   - 限制符号链接跟随\n\n2. **文件权限**\n   - 验证文件可读性\n   - 验证目录可写性（用于输出）\n   - 不处理敏感文件（如 `.ssh`、`.aws`）\n\n3. **元数据安全**\n   - 不在日志中输出敏感信息\n   - 支持环境变量覆盖\n   - 验证端口范围（1-65535）\n\n4. **依赖安全**\n   - 仅读取依赖文件，不执行\n   - 不验证依赖完整性（由 build 命令处理）\n   - 警告使用不安全的依赖\n\n5. **Dockerfile 安全**\n   - 使用官方基础镜像\n   - 非 root 用户运行\n   - 最小化镜像层\n   - 健康检查配置\n\n## Performance Considerations\n\n1. **文件 I/O**\n   - 最小化文件系统访问\n   - 使用缓存避免重复读取\n   - 并行处理多个文件（如果适用）\n\n2. **内存使用**\n   - 流式处理大文件\n   - 避免不必要的数据复制\n   - 使用生成器而非列表\n\n3. **启动时间**\n   - 延迟加载非核心模块\n   - 优化导入\n   - 减少初始化开销\n\n4. **并发处理**\n   - 异步文件 I/O（如果适用）\n   - 并行验证多个文件\n\n## Monitoring and Metrics\n\n### 日志\n\n使用 Python 标准日志模块：\n\n```python\nimport logging\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n```\n\n**日志级别**:\n- `DEBUG`: 详细调试信息\n- `INFO`: 一般信息（进度、成功消息）\n- `WARNING`: 警告信息\n- `ERROR`: 错误信息\n- `CRITICAL`: 严重错误\n\n### 进度显示\n\n使用 Rich `Progress` 组件：\n\n```python\nfrom rich.progress import Progress, SpinnerColumn\n\nwith Progress(\n    SpinnerColumn(),\n    *Progress.get_default_columns(),\n) as progress:\n    task = progress.add_task(\"[green]Packing agent...\", total=100)\n    # 更新进度\n```\n\n### 错误追踪\n\n- 使用 Python 标准异常\n- 提供详细的错误消息\n- 支持 verbose 模式的完整堆栈\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持更多编程语言？\n   - **当前**: 仅支持 Python 和 Java\n   - **讨论**: Go、Node.js 等语言需求\n   - **决策**: 初始仅支持 Python 和 Java，后续根据需求添加\n\n2. **Q2**: 是否需要支持自定义 Dockerfile 模板？\n   - **当前**: 使用内置模板\n   - **讨论**: 用户可能需要自定义模板\n   - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n\n3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持依赖自动下载？\n   - **当前**: 仅验证依赖文件\n   - **讨论**: 自动下载可提高用户体验\n   - **决策**: 不支持，由 build 命令处理\n\n4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持工作区模板？\n   - **当前**: 用户手动创建工作区\n   - **讨论**: 预定义模板可简化初始化\n   - **决策**: 考虑添加 `init` 命令\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. 实现 Phase 1-2（基础结构和元数据模型）\n2. 实现 Phase 3（元数据服务）\n3. 实现 Phase 4（PackRuntime）\n4. 实现 Phase 5（CLI 命令集成）\n5. 实现 Phase 6（Dockerfile 模板）\n6. 实现 Phase 7（测试）\n7. 实现 Phase 8（文档）\n8. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n\n## References\n\n- [AgentCube CLI Spec](../cli-toolkit/spec.md)\n- [AgentCube CLI Design](../cli-toolkit/design.md)\n- [Typer Documentation](https://typer.tiangolo.com/)\n- [Pydantic Documentation](https://docs.pydantic.dev/)\n- [Rich Documentation](https://rich.readthedocs.io/)\n- [Docker Best Practices](https://docs.docker.com/develop/dev-best-practices/)\n- [Python Packaging Guide](https://packaging.python.org/)\n- [Maven Documentation](https://maven.apache.org/guides/)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775864717011,"end":1775864717020}}}}
